    • subSequence

      public BasicSourceTokenSequence subSequence(int fromIndex, int toIndex)
      Creates a new token sequence that is a subset of this sequence.

      The returned token sequence is independent from this sequence. Any changes in the returned sequence are not reflected in this sequence, and vice-versa.

      Parameters:
      fromIndex - Low token index (inclusive) of the sub sequence
      toIndex - High token index (exclusive) of the sub sequence
      Returns:
      A new token sequence that is a subset of this sequence
